function defaultRecipient(l,channel){if(!l)return"";if(channel==="whatsapp"||channel==="sms"){let p=((channel==="whatsapp"&&l.whatsapp)||l.phone||"").split("|")[0].replace(/\D/g,"");if(p.startsWith("0"))p="98"+p.slice(1);return p}return""}
